<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Forest Project</title>
		<script
			src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/bf215725e5.js"
			crossorigin="anonymous"
		></script>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
		<link href="./dist/css/hamburgers.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />

		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./dist/css/style.min.css" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<!-- @include 'nav.kit' -->

		<section class="offer-page">
			<h1 class="offer-page__title">Nasze oferty</h1>
			<div class="offer-page__card">
				<div class="offer-page__card-img img-one"></div>
				<div class="offer-page__card-box">
					<h3 class="offer-page__card-box__title">Strengthen Family Bonds</h3>
					<p class="offer-page__card-box__paragraph">
						The essence of a family adventure offer lies in the quality time it
						provides for families to reconnect. Away from the distractions of
						everyday life, families can engage in meaningful conversations,
						share laughter, and create cherished memories. Bonding over shared
						adventures and overcoming challenges together fosters a sense of
						unity and strengthens the familial bond. Whether it's conquering a
						hiking trail as a team or supporting each other in a thrilling zip
						line adventure, these experiences create a strong sense of
						camaraderie.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="offer-page__card">
				<div class="offer-page__card-img img-two"></div>
				<div class="offer-page__card-box">
					<h3 class="offer-page__card-box__title">
						Create Everlasting Memories:
					</h3>
					<p class="offer-page__card-box__paragraph">
						The moments shared during a family adventure become stories that are
						recounted with fondness for years to come. These adventures provide
						ample opportunities for capturing candid family photographs against
						stunning backdrops, preserving the joy and excitement forever.
						Imagine the smiles on your children’s faces as they conquer their
						fears, the laughter shared around a campfire, and the sense of
						achievement after completing a challenging trek. These memories
						become a treasure trove, reminding your family of the incredible
						bond you share.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="offer-page__card">
				<div class="offer-page__card-img img-three"></div>
				<div class="offer-page__card-box">
					<h3 class="offer-page__card-box__title">
						Professional Guidance and Safety
					</h3>
					<p class="offer-page__card-box__paragraph">
						Safety is paramount in any adventure, especially when it involves
						your loved ones. Proffesstional adventure offers typically come with
						professional guides and instructors who ensure that every activity
						is conducted with the highest safety standards. Whether you are
						exploring dense jungles, kayaking down rivers, or embarking on a
						wildlife safari, you can rest assured that experts are by your side,
						ensuring a secure and enjoyable experience for everyone.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="offer-page__card">
				<div class="offer-page__card-img img-four"></div>
				<div class="offer-page__card-box">
					<h3 class="offer-page__card-box__title">
						Health and Wellness Benefits
					</h3>
					<p class="offer-page__card-box__paragraph">
						Adventure vacations offer more than just mental and emotional
						benefits; they contribute to your family’s overall well-being.
						Physical activities such as hiking, swimming, and cycling not only
						provide a cardiovascular workout but also strengthen muscles and
						improve flexibility. Engaging in outdoor adventures promotes a
						healthy lifestyle, encouraging your family to stay active and
						embrace wellness. Moreover, being surrounded by nature has been
						proven to reduce stress, enhance mood, and boost overall mental
						health.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="offer-page__card">
				<div class="offer-page__card-img img-five"></div>
				<div class="offer-page__card-box">
					<h3 class="offer-page__card-box__title">Unplug and Reconnect</h3>
					<p class="offer-page__card-box__paragraph">
						In a world dominated by screens and notifications, a family
						adventure offer encourages families to unplug from their devices and
						reconnect with each other and with nature. The absence of
						distractions allows for genuine interactions and meaningful
						conversations. It's a chance for parents to truly engage with their
						children, sharing stories, playing games, and rediscovering the joy
						of being fully present in the moment. Unplugging from the digital
						world leads to a deeper connection within the family unit.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<!-- @include 'footer.kit' -->
		<script src="./dist/js/main.min.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>
